            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row border-top border-light mx-xl-5 py-4">
            <div class="col-md-6 px-xl-0">
                <p class="mb-md-0 text-center text-md-left text-dark">
                    &copy; <a class="text-dark font-weight-semi-bold" href="#">Made by Group <span class="text-primary">8</span> D3 TI 22 with all we are  heart <span style="color: red;">❤️</span></a>
